Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:35.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.75,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:40.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,死者即是过往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:49.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,不可能再和活着的人有任何交集了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:01.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,就算留下来 也没有任何作用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:03.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,再也没法去往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:05.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你可以消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,这点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你也已经一无所有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,不 你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,刚才不是想和我对刺同归于尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.89,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:11.02,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,一切的一切都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:15.07,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:24.36,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,要是你不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:37.03,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,要是你不存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.20,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,你这死神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:42.82,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你已经
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,不用再被我束缚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,已经可以把我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:51.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.55,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,吃早饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:01.55,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.11,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.51,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,你一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.95,Sub-CN-UP,,0,0,0,,既没有事物待守
